{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_12_01",
  "title": "神崎莉央",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……前の仕事が押したから、次の現場への到着は\n少し遅れそうね……。あら、葵からメッセがきたわ",
      "startTime": 5.9811377343,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3552.195599,
          "startTime": 9.5333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 5.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.5666655858
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "愛とこころも到着したそうよ\n「コメント録りは先に始めててちょうだい」――っと",
      "startTime": 14.5666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3030.3344965,
          "startTime": 14.5970000823
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6700.001080900001,
          "startTime": 18.2666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "今日はついに……あの番組の撮影ですね\n莉央さん、緊張してますか？",
      "startTime": 23.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.1423345566
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "別に、そんなに身構えてはいないわよ\nむしろ、こんな番組観てくれる人いるのかしら",
      "startTime": 29.8423356374,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです。BIG4になって\nファンがますます増えたおかげで……",
      "startTime": 36.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.2436269443
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "新しいファンから「過去のリズノワを知りたい」って\n要望が沢山届いたんでしょ。何度も聞いたわよ",
      "startTime": 42.8769613584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.9769587517
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "私達の仕事は、ファンの声に応えることだし\nドキュメンタリーを撮るのは構わない。でも名前が……",
      "startTime": 51.3436264992,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "俺が考えた『LizNoir・BIG4までの軌跡\n～アイドルを夢見たっていいじゃない～』ですか？",
      "startTime": 61.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.3691582044
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "恥ずかしいわよ、そのタイトル……貴方って\n仕事は出来るのに、こういうセンスは全然ないのね",
      "startTime": 67.9358274778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "せめてその恥ずかしいサブタイトルだけは\n外してちょうだい。いいわね？",
      "startTime": 74.4691608112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.1024900119
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いいタイトルだと思ったんですが……分かりました\nカットします。あ、そろそろロケ現場に到着しますよ",
      "startTime": 81.4434946067,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 87.4268479348
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 87.4268479348
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "……バンプロのオフィス、か\nまさか、こんな形で古巣に来ることになるとはね",
      "startTime": 92.7601822854,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 88.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "久しぶりのバンプロですね。どうですか？\nやっぱり、懐かしいですか？",
      "startTime": 100.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 102.5748036703
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "……そうね。私が最初に入った事務所であり\nリズノワが生まれた場所だもの",
      "startTime": 107.5414744696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "そして、あの人……葵と私を会わせてくれた\n私をアイドルにしてくれた人と出会った場所でもあるわ",
      "startTime": 116.374807803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 120.4748036703
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "今ここにはいないけど……\nあの人なしに、私達は生まれなかった",
      "startTime": 123.074807803,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5100.0031154,
          "startTime": 125.5748067857
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-shj001.m4a",
      "text": "ははははっ、そこまで言われると照れ臭いだろ\n……久しぶりだな、莉央",
      "startTime": 133.0748067857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 135.3748036703
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さん！？　……ちょっと{user}さん\n三枝さんが来るなんて、聞いてないわよ",
      "startTime": 139.3414734524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 142.241470337
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "だって三枝さんは、リズノワを生み出した人で\nリズノワを語るなら、不可欠な存在でしょう",
      "startTime": 145.9883127436,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-shj002.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワがデビューしてすぐ、バンプロを辞めた俺には\n過ぎた言葉だな。全ては彼女達自身の成果だ",
      "startTime": 153.0870288214,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 159.5870257061
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんが私達を置いて行ったのは納得出来ないけど\n私と葵を引き合わせてくれたことは感謝してますから",
      "startTime": 164.0203621548,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 168.0870307923
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "……まぁ、こんな所でピリピリしても仕方がないわね\nでも、どうして三枝さんが来ることを黙っていたの？",
      "startTime": 172.8536954881,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "すみません。当日まで三枝さんの仕事の都合がつくか\n分からなかったので……",
      "startTime": 181.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 183.2019511224
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-shj003.m4a",
      "text": "大切な仕事だからな、都合もつけるさ。それより\nさっき愛に聞いたんだが、葵がいなくなったらしいぞ",
      "startTime": 188.6352824849,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-shj004.m4a",
      "text": "どうやら機材トラブルで撮影が止まったらしくてね\n休憩の合間に踊りに行くと言って出て行ったそうだ",
      "startTime": 198.5686158182,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 203.2019511224
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　すぐに機材が復旧したら、どうするのよ\nスタッフさん達を待たせちゃうじゃない",
      "startTime": 206.9019491515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、葵らしいですけどね。俺、探してきますよ\n三枝さん、少しの間現場をよろしくお願いします",
      "startTime": 215.0831795905,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 218.8097286543
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "近くの公園を探してみるといいわ。バンプロにいた頃は\nよくあそこに逃走して一人で踊っていたから",
      "startTime": 223.3430600168,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7256.938012400014,
          "startTime": 226.0666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 226.9430670739
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
