      "text": "（莉央さんの助言のおかげで、葵の捕獲に成功した俺は）\n（莉央さんのコメント録りになんとか間に合った）",
      "startTime": 241.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "はい、一旦、ここで休憩に入ります\n莉央さん、お疲れ様です。飲み物をどうぞ",
      "startTime": 247.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 251.4328172048
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。別に疲れてはいないわよ\n葵を探して走り回ってた貴方に比べたら",
      "startTime": 255.1661434811,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "でも……疲れはしないけど、昔話をするのは\n少し恥ずかしいわね。貴方と初めて会った時のこととか",
      "startTime": 263.4994829179,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 268.6328233083
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "あの時は衝撃でした。「もうすぐいなくなる人の名刺を\n持っている意味はないでしょ？」って言われて……",
      "startTime": 273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 276.1997618358
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんなこともあったわね。あの時は私\n少しピリピリしてたから……悪いと思ってるわ",
      "startTime": 280.733088112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "いえ。そりゃ少し驚きましたけど、あの頃の莉央さんが\nいろんなものを抱え込んでたって、今は知ってますから",
      "startTime": 289.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 293.8498297374
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。私達がデビューしてすぐ、信頼していた\n三枝さんがバンプロを辞めてしまって……",
      "startTime": 299.1831560136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio022.m4a",
      "text": "それ以来、私が心から信じられる存在は、お母さんと\n……葵だけだったわ",
      "startTime": 308.6831560136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 310.6498195649
    },
    {
