      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio023.m4a",
      "text": "それ以外の人達には、デビュー以来ずっと\n壁を作っていたから。貴方に対してもそうだった",
      "startTime": 313.7831560136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 318.5164862316
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio024.m4a",
      "text": "……ごめんなさい。雰囲気を暗くしちゃって\n気分を変えて、とっておきの話をさせてもらえる？",
      "startTime": 322.0498226803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
